{
  "stem": "24195.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you hear the enemy artillery fire in the distance.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What are you going to do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, they're-- if they're already on German grounds, and they're coming, we're in the center of Germany, at this [GERMAN], you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's not a good sign, so-- for them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they had to-- nobody-- the last few days went without you know, no-- any incidents of brutal-- well, there was never really any serious incident of brutality.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But they-- they even became more relaxed and friendly, because they were thinking now, what-- what are they going to do, if those troops arrive here?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they're going to be all made prisoners, because they're paramilitary, or men in uniforms.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, they're considered to be a military personnel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So then-- I think it was August-- March-- no, it was April now.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was April 12th-- April 11th or 12th, 1945, when they decided that that fire had become-- the artillery fire had become much stronger.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In fact, on April 12th or 13-- I forget now.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "April 11th?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I'm not quite sure the exact date, but it was around that time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Suddenly, we could hear small arms fire.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It sounded like machine gun fire and so forth.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Now, if you can hear machine gun fire and rifle shot fire, you know those troops are not very far from you.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that day, they decided to-- the guards decided, and the order came through from the SS major-- the camp has to be evacuated.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was only one place left to evacuate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All the western part of Germany was already occupied.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Bavaria was the only place that was the-- that was to the southeast.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the order comes out-- everybody get ready.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They're going to put us on-- on trucks.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
